{"tid":1041942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1遭警鎖手銬 兩示威者索償敗訴","createTime":"2019-03-01T08:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T12:31:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"493e0a2b6fe7cbfe37bc7f1d74322d393d07b86c","tid":1041942,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190301/20623395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190301%2F20623395&d=oVHkeUedSvD9nF4ig%2BuBMBdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=2c822d49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190301%2F20623395&h=a5d81240\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190301/20623395</a><br />\n<br />\n7.1遭警鎖手銬 兩示威者索償敗訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190301/large/img_0709.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190301%2Flarge%2Fimg_0709.jpg&h=e747169c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申索人梁國華（左）和關振邦原本各索償5萬元，結果每人須向政府賠償1.2萬元訟費。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】國家主席習近平前年7.1訪港，尖沙嘴文化中心有示威，兩名社運人士質疑警方無理拘捕，濫用手銬，循小額錢債審裁處控告警方。審裁官昨判兩人敗訴，認為警方有基礎懷疑兩人阻礙文娛中心職員執行職務，而且當日示威並不和平，申索人曾激動反抗，警方為保自身和他人安全，防範申索人逃走，有必要動用手銬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每人須賠政府1.2萬<br />\n<br />\n申索人梁國華和關振邦原本各索償5萬元，結果每人須向政府賠償1.2萬元訟費。梁質疑涉案證人以公職人員身份出庭，為何訟費包括工資損失，審裁官指案例表明須彌補政府因證人出庭而蒙受的損失。審裁官指當日示威者拉起大幅橫額，文化中心職員勸喻離開，但申索人大聲喝罵，肢體反抗，又有人推鐵馬，場面混亂，關一度跌倒。審裁官認為警方有理由相信申索人涉嫌違法，即使兩人最終沒被起訴，也不代表拘捕無理，至於警員沒展示委任證並非重點。審裁官續指，警方用手銬鎖住申索人，乘警車用7分鐘返回警署，確認安全便解除，合理合法。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：SCTC42079-80/17<br />\n■記者勞東來  <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n安排外傭假結婚 女主腦入獄39月<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n昨晚六合彩開獎結果"},{"pid":"9396510828f2a9685b37187b4816973599384e24","tid":1041942,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1a8570d8987ce494a6813aca3d8c0101696a4164","tid":1041942,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:26:03.000Z","msg":"即使兩人最終沒被起訴，也不代表拘捕無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a9185d93cc2d2a22ed04e2f1ac1a92af9ef73a","tid":1041942,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"至於警員沒展示委任證並非重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fce880fcbd6a7e6343358e098eca146f09b535f","tid":1041942,"uid":49609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3a9185d93cc2d2a22ed04e2f1ac1a92af9ef73a","tid":1041942,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"至於警員沒展示委任證並非重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"去過小額錢債就知啲審裁官咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2015cf80c492968c2d29d554cc905cfac52ca07d","tid":1041942,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fce880fcbd6a7e6343358e098eca146f09b535f","tid":1041942,"uid":49609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3a9185d93cc2d2a22ed04e2f1ac1a92af9ef73a","tid":1041942,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T08:31:10.000Z","msg":"至於警員沒展示委任證並非重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T09:11:07.000Z","msg":"去過小額錢債就知啲審裁官咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:15:40.000Z","msg":"原來咁垃圾"},{"pid":"772446feb00fbaf5ce66e103a0cf50f9284777b4","tid":1041942,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fce880fcbd6a7e6343358e098eca146f09b535f","tid":1041942,"uid":49609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3a9185d93cc2d2a22ed04e2f1ac1a92af9ef73a","tid":1041942,"uid"